Author: lotsofsqs
Text: I hear you. I remember getting my first Vogue in middle school and realizing this. It was life changing, honestly.  I've got the same body type as Lana del Rey right now, so I'm trying to amp up American glam looks rather than the high fashion stuff I love so much.

Author: bannaberry
Text: This is me. My Pinterest is filled with outfits I would love to wear on body types I strive to have.
